me I bought BustedBus arms with new ball joints pre installed

> Be careful on how this is done.  Pulling the ball joints can be done
> using rented tools. Replacing the ball joints, however, requires a
> special tool and heavy duty press to swage over the top of the ball
> joint onto the arm.  If this isn't done the ball joint could pull out of
> the arm at maximum downward travel.  

